name: Snoopy's Magic Show [GB]
description: Snoopy's Magic Show (スヌーピーのマジックショー, Snoopy no Magic Show), also known as Snoopy: Magic Show, is an Action puzzle video game based on the Snoopy cartoon characters licensed from Peanuts. It was developed and published by Kemco, which was released for the Game Boy in 1990.
